    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable, no-frills daily driver. While it remains mechanically functional, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the roof and hood. The interior is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some of the plastic trim. It has been regularly serviced, and though it lacks modern tech and has these cosmetic imperfections, it starts up reliably and handles everyday commuting without issue. Expect a solid car that prioritizes function over form.",
      "price": 21500.0,
