    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still got so much life left in it! It runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. It\u2019s in really solid shape and honestly a total joy to drive. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
