    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure chassis longevity, the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were addressed as preventative maintenance. The suspension retains its sharp turn-in characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a precise steering rack. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-driven machine, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
