    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained executive sedan that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Sapphire Blue Metallic that retains a high-gloss luster; upon close inspection, you will find only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. The alloy wheels are curb-rash free and wrapped in premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple black leather upholstery. The driver\u2019s seat shows light, natural bolster wear consistent with careful use, while the rear seats look virtually new. All tech features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is sound, featuring a complete service history with a recent fluid flush and brake pad replacement. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been garaged and loved.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
